    /* â•â•â• DEVICE CARDS â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
    .device-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--r-md); padding: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; transition: all var(--tx); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .device-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: var(--border-strong); }
    .device-card.device-online::before { background: var(--green); }
    .device-card.device-offline::before { background: var(--red); }
    .device-card.device-idle::before { background: var(--amber); }
    .device-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-strong); box-shadow: var(--sh-sm); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .device-head { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; gap: 10px; }
    .device-name { font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -0.005em; }
    .device-type { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-subtle); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; margin-top: 2px; }
    .device-status { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; }
    .device-status--online { background: var(--green-muted); border: 1px solid var(--green-border); color: var(--green); }
    .device-status--offline { background: var(--red-muted); border: 1px solid var(--red-border); color: var(--red); }
    .device-status--idle { background: var(--amber-muted); border: 1px solid var(--amber-border); color: var(--amber); }
    .device-status__dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: currentColor; }
    .device-metrics { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 6px; }
    .dm-item { background: var(--bg-muted); border-radius: var(--r-sm); padding: 8px 10px; }
    .dm-item .dm-lbl { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.11em; color: var(--text-subtle); }
    .dm-item .dm-val { font-size: 14.5px; font-weight: 700; font-family: var(--fm); color: var(--text); margin-top: 1px; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
    .dm-item .dm-sub { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--text-subtle); }
    .device-footer { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); gap: 8px; }
    .device-footer small { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-subtle); font-family: var(--fm); }

    /* â•â•â• SECTION DIVIDER â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
    .section-divider { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin: 4px 0; }
    .section-divider::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }
    .section-divider span { font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--text-subtle); white-space: nowrap; }
    .section-block { scroll-margin-top: calc(var(--header-h) + 14px); }

    /* â•â•â• STAT COMPARE â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
    .stat-compare { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .sc-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
    .sc-item .sc-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 11px; }
    .sc-item .sc-head span { color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 500; }
    .sc-item .sc-head strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; font-family: var(--fm); }
    .sc-track { height: 6px; background: var(--bg-muted); border-radius: 4px; position: relative; }
    .sc-range { position: absolute; top: 0; height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; }
    .sc-dot { position: absolute; top: -2px; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--text); border: 2px solid var(--bg-card); transform: translateX(-50%); box-shadow: var(--sh-xs); }

    /* â•â•â• EMPTY / LANDING â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
    .empty-state { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; padding: 80px 32px; gap: 14px; }
    .empty-state h2 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
    .empty-state p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 340px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .product-page { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 32px; }
    .landing-hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
    @@media (max-width: 700px) { .landing-hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .landing-hero h1 { font-size: 44px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.035em; line-height: 1.05; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .landing-hero p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .hero-note { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--r-lg); padding: 22px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .hero-note strong { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 10px; display: block; }
    .hero-note span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .hero-note span::before { content: ''; width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent-muted); border: 1.5px solid var(--accent); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .solution-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
    @@media (max-width: 700px) { .solution-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .page-hero { padding: 40px 0; }
    .page-hero h1 { font-size: 34px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .page-hero p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .eyebrow-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-muted); border: 1px solid #93C5FD; border-radius: 20px; padding: 3px 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; }

    /* ─── Dashboard: nav pill width = workspace (cards) width ──────── */
    @@media (min-width: 1101px) {
        .global-nav { left: var(--rail); }
        .global-nav__inner { max-width: none; margin: 0; }
        .side-rail {
            margin-top: -50px;
            height: calc(100vh + 50px);
            min-height: calc(100vh + 50px);
            top: 10px;
        }
    }

    /* ─── Rail head (always visible, nav scrolls below it) ──────── */
    .rail-head {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        background: var(--bg-card);
        padding: 14px 14px 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .rail-head__badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        font-family: var(--fm);
        font-size: 9px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent);
        background: var(--accent-muted);
        border: 1px solid rgba(26,86,219,.2);
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 2px 6px;
        margin-bottom: 7px;
    }
    .rail-head__meta {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 6px;
        margin: 8px 0 10px;
    }
    .rail-chip {
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 6px 8px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    }
    .rail-chip__label {
        display: block;
        font-size: 9px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--text-subtle);
    }
    .rail-chip__value {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 2px;
