            @* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
                   DATA SOURCE BAR — what we're analysing, how it looks
                   â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• *@
            <div class="datasource u-fade-up u-d1" id="datasource-bar">
                <div class="datasource__group">
                    <div class="datasource__item">
                        <span class="datasource__lbl">Zdroj dát</span>
                        <span class="datasource__val"><strong>NestStats Supabase</strong> · telemetry_live</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="datasource__item">
                        <span class="datasource__lbl">Interval vzorkovania</span>
                        <span class="datasource__val" id="ds-sampling">~60 s</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="datasource__item">
                        <span class="datasource__lbl">Počet bodov v okne</span>
                        <span class="datasource__val" id="ds-points">@dashboard.History.Count</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="datasource__item">
                        <span class="datasource__lbl">Okno</span>
                        <span class="datasource__val">@dashboard.RangeStartLocal.ToString("dd.MM HH:mm") – @dashboard.RangeEndLocal.ToString("dd.MM HH:mm")</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="datasource__item">
                        <span class="datasource__lbl">Čerstvosť</span>
                        <span class="datasource__val" id="ds-freshness">@FreshnessAgo(dashboard.DataFreshnessMinutes)</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="datasource__item datasource__item--refresh">
                        <span class="datasource__lbl">@T("Automatická obnova", "Auto refresh")</span>
                        <div class="datasource-refresh">
                            <input class="datasource-refresh__range"
                                   id="quiet-refresh-minutes"
                                   type="range"
                                   min="1"
                                   max="11"
                                   step="1"
                                   value="5"
                                   aria-label="@T("Interval automatickej obnovy", "Auto refresh interval")" />
                            <span class="datasource__val datasource-refresh__value" id="quiet-refresh-value">5 min</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="datasource__item">
                        <span class="datasource__lbl">@T("Inštalovaný výkon FV", "Installed PV capacity")</span>
                        <span class="datasource__val">@dashboard.InstalledPvKw.ToString("0.0", currency) kWp · @T("batéria", "battery") @dashboard.BatteryCapacityKwh.ToString("0.0", currency) kWh</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            @* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
                   #overview — FULL-WIDTH MAIN CHART
                   â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• *@
            <div class="section-block" id="overview">
                <article class="main-chart u-fade-up u-d2">
