            @* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
                   #flow — energy topology + savings
                   â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• *@
            <div class="grid-32 section-block flow-shell" id="flow">
                <article class="panel flow-shell__primary">
                    <div class="panel-head"><div><span class="eyebrow">Tok energie — live</span><h2>Aktuálne prúdenie</h2></div></div>
                    @{
                        var pvFlowClass = dashboard.LatestPvKw > 0.05 ? "is-active is-forward" : "is-idle";
                        var flowHomeKw = Math.Max(0, dashboard.LatestConsumptionKw - dashboard.LatestWattKw);
                        var homeFlowClass = flowHomeKw > 0.05 ? "is-active is-forward" : "is-idle";
                        var gridFlowClass = Math.Abs(dashboard.LatestGridKw) > 0.05
                            ? (dashboard.LatestGridKw < -0.05 ? "is-active is-forward" : "is-active is-reverse")
                            : "is-idle";
                        var batteryFlowClass = Math.Abs(dashboard.LatestBatteryKw) > 0.05
                            ? (dashboard.LatestBatteryKw < -0.05 ? "is-active is-forward" : "is-active is-reverse")
                            : "is-idle";
                        var wattFlowClass = dashboard.LatestWattKw > 0.05 ? "is-active is-forward" : "is-idle";
                    }
                    <div class="flow-graph">
                        <div class="flow-links" aria-hidden="true">
                            <span class="flow-link flow-link--pv @pvFlowClass" id="flow-link-pv"></span>
                            <span class="flow-link flow-link--grid @gridFlowClass" id="flow-link-grid"></span>
                            <span class="flow-link flow-link--home @homeFlowClass" id="flow-link-home"></span>
                            <span class="flow-link flow-link--bat @batteryFlowClass" id="flow-link-battery"></span>
                            <span class="flow-link flow-link--watt @wattFlowClass" id="flow-link-watt"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fn fn--pv">
                            <span class="fn__lbl">FV pole</span>
                            <strong id="flow-pv-kw">@Kw(dashboard.LatestPvKw)</strong>
                            <span id="flow-pv-note">@dashboard.CurrentPvSaturationPct.ToString("0.0", currency) % @T("z", "of") @dashboard.InstalledPvKw.ToString("0.0", currency) kWp</span>
                            <div class="fn-meter"><span id="flow-pv-fill" style="width:@dashboard.CurrentPvSaturationPct.ToString("0.0", CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)%"></span></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fn fn--inv">
                            <span class="fn__lbl">Menič / inverter</span>
                            <strong id="flow-inverter-kw">@Kw(dashboard.LatestInverterKw)</strong>
                            <span id="flow-inverter-note">@T("DC → AC konverzia", "DC → AC conversion")</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fn fn--home">
                            <span class="fn__lbl">Domácnosť</span>
                            <strong id="flow-home-kw">@Kw(flowHomeKw)</strong>
                            <span id="flow-home-note">@T("Odber", "Load")</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fn fn--grid">
                            <span class="fn__lbl">Distribučná sieť</span>
                            <strong id="flow-grid-kw">@Kw(dashboard.LatestGridKw)</strong>
                            <span id="flow-grid-note">@GridDir(dashboard.LatestGridKw)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fn fn--bat">
                            <span class="fn__lbl">Batéria</span>
                            <strong id="flow-battery-kw">@Kw(dashboard.LatestBatteryKw)</strong>
                            <span id="flow-battery-note">@batterySoc.ToString("0")&nbsp;% SOC · @BatDir(dashboard.LatestBatteryKw)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fn fn--watt">
                            <span class="fn__lbl">WattRouter</span>
                            <strong id="flow-watt-kw">@Kw(dashboard.LatestWattKw)</strong>
                            <span id="flow-watt-note" data-no-translate>@dashboard.CurrentWattUtilizationPct.ToString("0.0", currency) % @T("vyťaženie", "utilization") | @dashboard.RelayStates.Count(r => r.IsOn) / @dashboard.RelayChannelCount @T("aktívne", "active")</span>
                            <div class="fn-meter"><span id="flow-watt-fill" style="width:@dashboard.CurrentWattUtilizationPct.ToString("0.0", CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)%"></span></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>

