            @* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
                   #relays — SSR / relay channels
                   â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• *@
            <div class="grid-split section-block" id="relays">
                @{
                    var relayStates = dashboard.RelayStates;
                    var relayActiveCount = relayStates.Count(r => r.IsOn);
                    var relayTotalCount = relayStates.Count;
                    var relayVariableCount = relayStates.Count(r => r.Mode == "variable");
                    var relayBinaryCount = relayStates.Count(r => r.Mode == "binary");
                    var relayTotalPowerKw = relayStates.Sum(r => r.PowerKw);
                    var relayAverageLoadPct = relayStates.Count > 0 ? relayStates.Average(r => r.LoadPercentage) : 0;
                    var relayPeak = relayStates.OrderByDescending(r => r.PowerKw).ThenByDescending(r => r.LoadPercentage).FirstOrDefault();
                    var relayReserveCount = Math.Max(0, relayTotalCount - relayActiveCount);
                    var relayGridClass = relayTotalCount switch
                    {
                        1 => "relay-grid relay-grid--single",
                        <= 3 => "relay-grid relay-grid--few",
                        >= 7 => "relay-grid relay-grid--dense",
                        _ => "relay-grid"
                    };
                    var relayModeSummary = relayVariableCount > 0
                        ? "Plynulé SSR + sekcie"
                        : "Sekciové relé";
                }
                <article class="panel">
                    <div class="panel-head">
                        <div><span class="eyebrow">@T("SSR / Relé kanály", "SSR / relay channels")</span><h2>@T("Aktívne výstupné kanály", "Active output channels")</h2></div>
                        <span class="panel-badge" id="relay-active-count">@relayActiveCount / @relayTotalCount @T("aktívnych", "active")</span>
                    </div>
                    @if (relayTotalCount == 0)
                    {
                    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-subtle)">Relé dáta nie sú dostupné. Skontrolujte pripojenie WattRouter modulu.</p>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                    <div class="@relayGridClass" id="relay-grid-live">
                        @foreach (var relay in relayStates)
                        {
                        <article class="relay-chip @(relay.IsOn ? "is-on" : null)">
                            <span>@relay.Name</span>
                            <strong>@relay.PowerKw.ToString("0.00") kW</strong>
                            <small>@relay.Detail</small>
                            <div class="relay-chip__track">
                                <span style="width:@relay.LoadPercentage.ToString("0.0", CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)%"></span>
                            </div>
                            <em>@relay.LoadPercentage.ToString("0.0")&nbsp;% @(relay.Mode == "variable" ? "modulácia" : "stav")</em>
                        </article>
                        }
                    </div>
                    }
                </article>
                <article class="panel">
                    <div class="panel-head">
                        <div><span class="eyebrow">@T("Kanály — detail", "Channels — detail")</span><h2>@T("Výkon a záťaž", "Power and load")</h2></div>
                    </div>
                    @if (relayTotalCount == 0)
                    {
                        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-subtle)">Žiadne relé dáta.</p>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                    <div class="kpi-grid">
                        <div class="kpi-cell"><span class="k-lbl">@T("Aktívne", "Active")</span><strong>@relayActiveCount / @relayTotalCount</strong></div>
                        <div class="kpi-cell"><span class="k-lbl">@T("Rezerva", "Reserve")</span><strong>@relayReserveCount @T("kan.", "ch.")</strong></div>
                        <div class="kpi-cell"><span class="k-lbl">@T("Plynulé / sekčné", "Variable / staged")</span><strong>@relayVariableCount / @relayBinaryCount</strong></div>
                        <div class="kpi-cell"><span class="k-lbl">@T("Celkový výkon", "Total power")</span><strong>@relayTotalPowerKw.ToString("0.00", currency) kW</strong></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-compare" style="margin-top:14px">
                        <div class="sc-item">
                            <div class="sc-head">
                                <span>@T("Priemerné vyťaženie kanálov", "Average channel utilization")</span>
                                <strong>@relayAverageLoadPct.ToString("0.0", currency) %</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sc-track">
                                <div class="sc-range" style="left:0;width:@relayAverageLoadPct.ToString("0.0", CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)%;background:var(--accent);opacity:0.55"></div>
                                <div class="sc-dot" style="left:@relayAverageLoadPct.ToString("0.0", CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)%;background:var(--accent)"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sc-item">
                            <div class="sc-head">
                                <span>@T("Najsilnejší kanál", "Strongest channel")</span>
                                <strong>@(relayPeak?.Name ?? "-") · @((relayPeak?.PowerKw ?? 0).ToString("0.00", currency)) kW</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sc-track">
